name: Insatiable Appetite For Love
description:
tw : light pixelated blood, language, descriptions of wounds

Hey! This is my first game I've like ever made in my life and because of that I really don't know how anything works. 

If you run into ANY issues or errors I will try to do my best to fix them (I probably won't know how to fix them :,)) Or if there are any spelling mistakes lmk (I didn't double check anything)

Okay so onto the actual stuff now.

This was made for frog jam 2022, featuring the first chapter of Jay's route. I plan to make other routes in the future, (I already have an idea for 2 different ones.) I also plan to go back and give this game a customized main screen and other stuff like that in the future. If you have any ideas for routes, stuff you want to see or suggestions please let me know it would help me out a lot!

Please enjoy!

<3

Made using Ren'py
